# REQUIREMENTS.md

On requirement / constraint / acceptance criterion / non-goal: persist to **`REQUIREMENTS.md`** (root, or `docs/REQUIREMENTS.md` if present).

- Read first; merge near-duplicates; strike or “Superseded by:” per file style.
- Use existing headings; don’t over-structure tiny files.
- Short testable bullets; MUST/SHOULD/IDs only if the file already uses them.
- Missing file: add title + `## Requirements`.
